    "SS2_DRONE_SHOCK_PICKUP": "<style=cIsUtility>电击</style>附近的敌人,打断并眩晕它们。",
    "SS2_DRONE_SHOCK_DESCRIPTION": "一种用金钱购买的同伴,会近距离跟随幸存者,<style=cIsUtility>电击</style>敌人,打断并眩晕它们。",
    "SS2_DRONE_SHOCK_SKILL_DESCRIPTION": "发射电击爆炸,在区域内造成<style=cIsDamage>100%伤害</style>并<style=cIsUtility>电击</style>敌人<style=cIsUtility>5秒</style>。",
    "SS2_DRONE_SHOCK_COMMAND_DESCRIPTION": "命令电击无人机电击附近的敌人。",
