    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXSUPERICE_PICKUP": "成为冰霜的先驱。",
    "SS2_ELITE_MODIFIER_SUPERLIGHTNING": "超载的 {0}",
    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXSUPERLIGHTNING_NAME": "风暴之眼（这不应该是风暴之子吗？）",
    "SS2_EQUIP_AFFIXSUPERLIGHTNING_PICKUP": "成为雷电的先驱。",
