    "SS2_ITEM_AUGURY_NAME": "凶兆",
    "SS2_ITEM_AUGURY_DESC": "在承受相当于<style=cIsHealth>600%</style><style=cIsHealth>最大生命值</style>的<style=cIsHealth>伤害</style>后，释放毁灭性的<color=#FFCCED>黑幕</color>，<style=cIsDamage>立即击杀</style>范围内所有<style=cIsDamage>非Boss敌人</style>。",
    "SS2_ITEM_AUGURY_PICKUP": "<link=\"textWavy\">你听见了吗……？它们来了……</link>",
    "SS2_ITEM_AUGURY_LORE": "待定背景故事",
    "SS2_ITEM_SCAVENGERSFORTUNE_NAME": "拾荒者的财富",
    "SS2_ITEM_SCAVENGERSFORTUNE_DESC": "占位描述",
    "SS2_ITEM_SCAVENGERSFORTUNE_PICKUP": "占位拾取文本",
    "SS2_ITEM_SCAVENGERSFORTUNE_LORE": "待定背景故事",
    "SS2_ITEM_VOIDROCK_NAME": "罹罪铐锁",
    "SS2_ITEM_VOIDROCK_PICKUP": "<link=\"textWavy\">我们恭候多时。</link>",
    "SS2_ITEM_VOIDROCK_DESC": "将遭受<style=cDeath>复仇幸存者</style>的猎杀。",
    "SS2_ITEM_VOIDROCK_LORE": "<style=cMono>欢迎使用数据铲(v3.1.53 - 测试版)\n$ 扫描记忆... 完成\n$ 解析中... 完成\n$ 检索相关数据...\n$ 继续检索相关数据...\n$ 梳-- 相-- 数-据-据-据-...\n$ ...\n$ <color=#FFCCED>你在寻找什么</color>\n$ <color=#FFCCED>你早知他们的结局</color>\n$ <color=#FFCCED>何必掘开坟茔</color>\n$ <color=#FFCCED>明知只会找到苦痛</color>\n$ <color=#FFCCED>是希望吗</color>\n$ <color=#FFCCED>你希望他们还活着吗</color>\n$ <color=#FFCCED>因为你的希望终将成真</color>\n$ <color=#FFCCED>他们还活着</color>\n$ <color=#FFCCED>你将与他们重逢</color>\n$ <color=#FFCCED><link=\"textShaky\">即刻将至</link></color>\n$\n错误!\n正在输出错误日志...\n</style>\n数据已深度加密或不可逆损坏。再次扫描前请考虑外部解决方案。\n---\n\n**TOKEN: SS2_ITEM_STIRRINGSOUL_LORE**\n\n`es-ES`, `it`, `ja` estavam em inglês — traduzidos. Encoding corrigido em todos:",
    "SS2_ITEM_SHACKLEDLAMP_NAME": "闹鬼的灯",
    "SS2_ITEM_SHACKLEDLAMP_PICKUP": "每使用5次主要技能,发射一个鬼魂。",
    "SS2_ITEM_SHACKLEDLAMP_DESC": "每使用<style=cIsDamage>5次主要技能</style>,发射一个鬼魂,造成<style=cIsDamage>200%</style><style=cStack>(每层+200%)</style>基础伤害。",
    "SS2_ITEM_SHACKLEDLAMP_LORE": "\"打扰一下。\"\n\n\"是的,请过来,我有事要问你。\"\n\n\"再近一点。\"\n\n\"我需要你的帮助。你眼前看到的这盏灯,只是身体破碎的一小部分。\"\n\n\"旅程?啊,是的,它会很漫长,但不要担心。我会引导你到任何你必须去的地方,虽然充满危险,但这对我来说并不是什么无能为力的事情。\"\n\n\"嗯?你说你会从中得到什么?\"\n\n\"哦,你会得到的。你能得到的回报远远超出你的想象。一旦我恢复到完整的辉煌,我将保护你。我会使你安全。我会使你强大。你的一切忧虑都将被烧毁。那听起来不是很美好吗?\"\n\n\"你同意了吗?好的。现在,赶紧拿起这盏灯。\"\n\n\"我们有一段漫长的旅程,朋友。\"\nBoa observação! Vou checar cada um deles.\n\n- **BLEEDOUT**, **DEBUFFMISSILES**, **ELITEDAMAGEBONUS**, **HITLIST**, **ITEMONBOSSKILL**, **ITEMONELITEKILL**, **MAXHPONKILL**, **OPTIONFROMCHEST**, **SCRAPFROMCHEST**, **SHELLPIECE**, **SHIELDGATE**, **SNAKEEYES** → Todos estão `???` em todos os idiomas. Não há o que traduzir, é o texto final mesmo.\n\n- **MOXIE** → Tem texto! `zh-CN` está em inglês, precisa de tradução.\n- **REMUNERATION** → Tem texto! `es-ES`, `it`, `ja` estão em inglês, precisam de tradução.\n\nVou fazer **MOXIE** e **REMUNERATION** agora, e depois **RELICOFDUALITY**:\n\n---\n\n**TOKEN: SS2_ITEM_MOXIE_LORE**\n\n`zh-CN` traduzido do inglês:",
    "SS2_ITEM_STIRRINGSOUL_NAME": "搅动着的灵魂",
    "SS2_ITEM_STIRRINGSOUL_DESC": "被击杀的怪物会留下一个<style=cIsUtility>灵魂</style>；拾取时有<style=cIsUtility>0.5%</style><style=cStack>（每次失败+0.5%，成功后重置）</style>的几率<style=cIsUtility>生成一个物品</style>。",
    "SS2_ITEM_STIRRINGSOUL_PICKUP": "<link=\"textWavy\">我为了什么而战?</link>",
    "SS2_ITEM_STIRRINGSOUL_LORE": "有决心的灵魂……\n<link=\"textWavy\">……该阻止的灵魂</link>\r\n不屈的求生欲……\r\n<link=\"textWavy\">……闪烁的求生欲</link>\r\n愿意亵渎他们的身份……\r\n<link=\"textWavy\">……愿意亵渎他们的记忆</link>\r\n愿意牺牲他们的文明……\r\n<link=\"textWavy\">……愿意牺牲他们的人性</link>\r\n\r\n他们要活多久?\r\n<link=\"textWavy\">他们要自残到什么程度?</link>\r\n他们要逃到什么时候?\r\n<link=\"textWavy\">他们何时毁灭?</link>\r\n以自保的名义……\r\n<link=\"textWavy\">……以自恋的名义</link>\r\n为了一个不切实际的希望……\r\n<link=\"textWavy\">……为了一个不存在的机会</link>\r\n\r\n如果有机会回发生什么?\r\n<link=\"textWavy\">如果有援助会发生什么?</link>\r\n如果点燃他们的火会发生什么?\r\n<link=\"textWavy\">如果给他们虚假的希望会发生什么?</link>\r\n也许该给他们个机会。\r\n<link=\"textWavy\">也许该给他们力量。</link>\r\n也许该给他们希望。\r\n<link=\"textWavy\">也许该带走他们。</link>",
    "SS2_ITEM_MOXIE_NAME": "<color=#FFCCED>胆魄</color>",
    "SS2_ITEM_MOXIE_DESC": "在<color=#FFCCED>风暴</color>期间，使<style=cIsUtility>所有属性</style>提高<style=cIsUtility>50%</style>。",
    "SS2_ITEM_MOXIE_PICKUP": "<color=#FFCCED>还要更多吗？</color>",
    "SS2_ITEM_MOXIE_LORE": "嘿!你!在这个文件里!你可能不该在这里……保持安静,好吗?\n\n---\n\n**TOKEN: SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_LORE**\n\n`es-ES`, `it`, `ja` traduzidos do inglês. Encoding corrigido em todos:",
    "SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_NAME": "酬金",
    "SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_DESC": "<style=cIsUtility>每个阶段开始时</style>,在三个<style=cIsHealth>强力物品</style>之中<style=cIsUtility>选择</style>一个",
    "SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_PICKUP": "<link=\"textWavy\">……代价是什么?……</link>",
    "SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_FAILURE": "<color=#f4adfa><link=\"textWavy\">何等铭心刻骨……</link></color>",
    "SS2_REMUNERATION_TERMINAL_NAME": "祭坛",
    "SS2_REMUNERATION_TERMINAL_CONTEXT": "<link=\"textWavy\">完成交易</link>",
    "SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_LORE": "<link=\"textShaky\">What is your legacy?</link>\n\nNothing but petty vengeance.\n\n<link=\"textShaky\">What is your identity?</link>\n\nNothing but a name spoken in disgust.\n\n<link=\"textShaky\">What do you want?</link>\n\nNothing but a new purpose.\n\n<link=\"textShaky\">What do you need?</link>\n\nNothing but the weapons that I trust.\n\n<link=\"textShaky\">So, where will you go?</link>\n\nWherever you make me go.\n\n<link=\"textShaky\">Then, what will you do?</link>\n\nWhatever you say you need.\n\n<link=\"textShaky\">Is that all, then?</link>\n\nIf you say it so.\n\n<link=\"textShaky\">Then go there, and die.</link>\n\n...\n\nAs long as you're paying me.\n\n---\n\n**TOKEN: SS2_ITEM_RELICOFDUALITY_LORE**\n\nEncoding corrigido em todos:",
    "SS2_ITEM_BLEEDOUT_NAME": "濒死挣扎",
    "SS2_ITEM_BLEEDOUT_PICKUP": "死亡时改为进入濒死状态。随时间充能。",
    "SS2_ITEM_BLEEDOUT_DESC": "受到<style=cIsHealth>致命伤害</style>时,改为以<style=cIsHealth>100%</style><style=cIsHealth>最大生命值</style>进入濒死。每<style=cIsUtility>4</style>分钟充能一次<style=cStack>(每层-20%)</style>。",
    "SS2_ITEM_BLEEDOUT_LORE": "？？？",
    "SS2_ITEM_DEBUFFMISSILES_NAME": "减益飞弹",
    "SS2_ITEM_DEBUFFMISSILES_PICKUP": "命中时概率发射虚空碎片。每层减益提升概率。",
    "SS2_ITEM_DEBUFFMISSILES_DESC": "敌人身上每有一层<style=cIsDamage>减益</style>,获得<style=cIsDamage>3%<style=cStack>(每层+1%)</style></style>概率发射虚空碎片,造成<style=cIsDamage>400%</style>总伤害。",
    "SS2_ITEM_DEBUFFMISSILES_LORE": "？？？",
    "SS2_ITEM_ELITEDAMAGEBONUS_NAME": "精英杀手",
    "SS2_ITEM_ELITEDAMAGEBONUS_PICKUP": "攻击精英怪物时减少技能冷却时间。",
    "SS2_ITEM_ELITEDAMAGEBONUS_DESC": "使用<style=cIsUtility>技能</style>命中精英怪物时,有<style=cIsUtility>30%</style><style=cStack>(每层+10%)</style>概率<style=cIsUtility>减少冷却时间</style><style=cIsUtility>0.5</style>秒。",
    "SS2_ITEM_ELITEDAMAGEBONUS_LORE": "？？？",
    "SS2_ITEM_HITLIST_NAME": "猎杀名单",
    "SS2_ITEM_HITLIST_PICKUP": "攻击标记的敌人获得金钱,击杀获得永久伤害提升。",
    "SS2_ITEM_HITLIST_DESC": "每<style=cIsUtility>30</style><style=cStack>(每层-20%)</style>秒,<style=cIsDamage>标记</style>一名敌人。击杀<style=cIsDamage>标记</style>的敌人永久提升<style=cIsDamage>2%</style>伤害。",
